uid":51446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紫薯, 芝士, 抹茶, 海膽</blockquote><br />\n放曬落煲到，四碗水煲埋一碗"},{"pid":"3b6cfc221b4b76a1ca934a342093c933834f8d1e","tid":96663,"uid":69133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:38:51.000Z","msg":"柯完屎放係馬桶<br />\n用屎既熱力焗佢15分鍾"},{"pid":"cafb854da04474e58008e138c3e9be660fe08cb9","tid":96663,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:47:26.000Z","msg":"要問呀b"},{"pid":"753aa22ceb7c6b77b1b2b46c2c3c44253e7a2b5e","tid":96663,"uid":79823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"抹茶沖水<br />\n海膽就咁食<br />\n芝士焗紫薯"},{"pid":"be69b454b6f1e39f90c56d8e8408a4c9a139d694","tid":96663,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"芝士撈海膽做成餡放入雪櫃6個鐘備用<br />\n紫薯壓成蓉做外皮 將餡包入去 搓圓壓扁再搓圓<br />\n最後沾上抹茶粉 用170度油炸 <br />\n芝士醬 拌碟"},{"pid":"f1bf020332981a93f7c9017c7af6de6f76785d24","tid":96663,"uid":43886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"洗乾淨紫薯<br />\n仔細去皮<br />\n切片<br />\n預備一個錫盤<br />\n盤底塗上一層薄薄的牛油<br />\n均衡的放上切好的紫薯<br />\n鋪上海膽<br />\n灑上雙色芝士粉<br />\n再灑上海鹽略以調味，備用。<br />\n<br />\n打開焗爐，220度預熱十分鐘。<br />\n及後以相同溫度放入紫薯。<br />\n待芝士呈現金黃色，略焦，即可取出。<br />\n<br />\n放置一分，即可灑上抹茶粉，<br />\n然後打開垃圾桶，向內傾倒。<br />\n再落m記買個豬柳強 ，即可。"},{"pid":"6c650b14de4bc180c8d704be4ed49f0822e043eb","tid":96663,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"全部放入攪拌機，加水榨汁飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fba9e835cab5558075db5b76aae3da16e1b23c3","tid":96663,"uid":27446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"塞晒入新假期試食員個口到"}]}